title: Unrealistic Entitlement ( Angela Rye and Manuel and Geiszel Godoy)
itunes:title: Unrealistic Entitlement ( Angela Rye and Manuel and Geiszel Godoy)
description:
Today on the show we had political pundit now turned ESPN correspondant Angela Rye stop by where she spoke about her new position At ESPN, NFL Rooney Rule, The Biden Administration, Brian Flores and so much more. Next, we had Manuel and Geiszel Godoy from "Black Sands Entertainemtent" and spoke about ancient black culture, black comics, Shark Tank and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a 23 inspiring rapper who got mad that no one answered Diddy's house, so he insisted on jumping Diddy's gate, but soon after tackled by security.
